{"tid":2448640,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「守護香港」召集人尹載道襲擊劉家衡及李文浩職員罪成 判刑四星期 准保釋等上訴","createTime":"2021-03-16T05:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T10:53:32.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ed02252d6755bcfd6f8bf38f69f95a9ff573f3b5","tid":2448640,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:17:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/localpresshk/19212\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flocalpresshk%2F19212&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=97fae10c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/localpresshk/19212</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第7庭 #陳佩妏暫委裁判官 #20200529長沙灣 #判刑 #普通襲擊 <br />\n<br />\n1200 「守護香港」召集人尹載道襲擊反對《港區國安法》街站案，裁判官閱畢社會服務令報告指被告冇悔意，判處服務令並不適合。考慮被告經審訊定罪，案發時情緒激動、手脚並用，直至警員到場並喝令乃停手，暴力程度不算輕微，且法庭不接納並判定被告解釋係捏作，被告事前更指罵議員、助理及其義工「人渣」、「垃圾」，而事發 2020 年社會氣氛仍然撕裂，有必要判處卽時監禁。量刑起點為四星期，冇理由緩刑、冇理由減刑，最終判刑一個月。 <br />\n<br />\n1204 被告代表律師申請以現金五百元取保等候上訴，晚十點後報到，理由為兼職餐廳「服務員」。 <br />\n<br />\n1205 裁判官要求日內繳交港幣五千圓、逢星期六晚九至十二時長沙灣警署報到，期間不得離開香港，退庭。"},{"pid":"82e84cd823b784dbc344de72728b81913226eeee","tid":2448640,"uid":150100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:19:07.000Z","msg":"花開了，然後凋零。星星是璀璨的，可那光芒也會消失。<br />\n這個地球、太陽、銀河系甚至連這個宇宙也會有死亡的時候。<br />\n人的一生和這些東西相比，簡直就像剎那間的事情，<br />\n在這樣的一瞬間，人降生了，笑著、哭著、憎恨、喜悅、悲傷、愛，<br />\n一切只是剎那間的邂逅，而最後都要歸入死的永眠。"},{"pid":"fd6904e12358be683242c0ea1281b31e7f816b91","tid":2448640,"uid":4493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"輕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adacc1ad48309f1981757dba41a5cdd2d8cd68f1","tid":2448640,"uid":52779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:20:44.000Z","msg":"DKLM"},{"pid":"c369d130345a454a21a2c0806db5399a2a9dcefa","tid":2448640,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd6904e12358be683242c0ea1281b31e7f816b91","tid":2448640,"uid":4493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"輕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:22:08.000Z","msg":"普通襲擊本身重極有限"},{"pid":"83a5aae1cc7d67fe9dee9628be93d1155b90edc4","tid":2448640,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:25:37.000Z","msg":"4星期咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5210fff56cb9e929334b8c3a3016fb0cbe8453","tid":2448640,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d1b4afc7fbc6d7d063995ab220e9115f5dfbb00","tid":2448640,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd6904e12358be683242c0ea1281b31e7f816b91","tid":2448640,"uid":4493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:19:12.000Z","msg":"輕到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:30:57.000Z","msg":"平時守行為就算"},{"pid":"00ee88747cde35a7d593131e78595b5574a72597","tid":2448640,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"4個月就差唔多"},{"pid":"b8ffc530ecb9340daf28d096e01ff38cacfd25e0","tid":2448640,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T06:17:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be988715899b1b2e23ce8792ec130e3b96aea6eb","tid":2448640,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T07:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00010c6d744605912a2c168c3d28545db5fbbe4","tid":2448640,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:36:30.000Z","msg":"裁判官又斥，被告自辯時「編作捏造」，他除喝罵事主為「人渣！垃圾！」外，所使用的暴力程度亦不算輕微，加上當時社會嚴重撕裂，故有必要判處監禁，考慮到本案案情及被告個人情況，最終判囚 4 星期。<br />\n<br />\n辯方隨即申請保釋等候上訴，<span class=\"red\">被告一度表示，無法即日交出數千元的保釋金，望法庭可給予一周時間籌錢</span>。不過，裁判官坦言「無得幾日喎，要交到（錢）先可以走」，被告最後答應即日繳付 5000 元，保釋期間不准離港，每週六往警署報到。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%8F%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99%E5%A5%B3%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%91%A8%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF-%E7%B7%A8%E4%BD%9C%E6%8D%8F%E9%80%A0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A1%2597%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF-%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258D%258F%25E9%2580%25A0%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=1dcdc69e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A1%2597%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF-%25E7%25B