t%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2595%2586%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A1%2597%25E7%25AB%2599%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258A%25A9%25E7%2590%2586-%25E5%2588%25A4%25E5%259B%259A-4-%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A8%25B4-%25E5%25AE%2598%25E6%2596%25A5%25E8%2587%25AA%25E8%25BE%25AF-%25E7%25B7%25A8%25E4%25BD%259C%25E6%258D%258F%25E9%2580%25A0%2F&h=1f511e4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E4%B8%AD%E5%B9%B4%E5%95%86%E4%BA%BA%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A%E5%8F%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E8%A1%97%E7%AB%99%E5%A5%B3%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86-%E5%88%A4%E5%9B%9A-4-%E5%91%A8%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B%E4%B8%8A%E8%A8%B4-%E5%AE%98%E6%96%A5%E8%87%AA%E8%BE%AF-%E7%B7%A8%E4%BD%9C%E6%8D%8F%E9%80%A0/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:39:19.000Z","msg":"講咁多咪又係俾到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6bdcc3e796364848b14ffe378b97ee1c53f7db","tid":2448640,"uid":235501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c832585cfc2875bd7f4ebb9177bb67c1d66376fd","tid":2448640,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T10:53:32.000Z","msg":"對於辯方稱被告向余「起右腳」是要勾着燈柱以保平衡，陳官不接納並斥說法荒誕無稽。陳官不接納事件純屬意外，或能預料余的介入會導致受傷，認為被告與余的接觸，力度不合理地過大和激烈，亦使余受驚，相信被告是惡意轉移襲擊目標。<br />\n<br />\n被告原本與劉家衡區議員秘書李譯喬共同被控當日在公眾地方打鬥，及後控方撤回對兩人的打鬥控罪，當時處理案件的裁判官林子勤看過事發片段後，認為李譯喬沒有自招嫌疑，批准李可取回訟費。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/YFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FYFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU%2F&d=HziU8jWK8j2Oa3ZLfTDirB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=550cfe84\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210316%2FYFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU%2F&h=b9287597\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210316/YFEFI2H5AFGNZDVCTSJYNBQHEU/</a>"}]}